and wash its entrails and its legs,

and put them with its pieces and its head,

29:18

and burn the whole ram on the altar.

It is a burnt offering to Yahweh.

It is a pleasing aroma, an offering by fire to Yahweh.

29:19

You shall take the other ram,

and Aharon and his sons shall lay their hands on the head of the ram.

29:20

